{"tid":1933770,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超 ： 最快4月30號才重開","createTime":"2020-03-19T13:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T13:17:14.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bb4238a0f98c5d850b28c5a726a38d141ea8876b","tid":1933770,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:16:49.000Z","msg":"因應武漢肺炎疫情於英國國內爆發，英超賽會及英格蘭足總上周召開緊急會議後，決定各級聯賽停擺至下月4日。而周四賽會再度召開會議，商討餘下的92場比賽如何完成。會後決定以一眾職球員的健康放在首位，聯賽重開之日將再一次推遲至4月30日，惟未有公佈任何實際措施解決球季停擺而衍生的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200319&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=60729119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200319%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D60729119&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=a222a0bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200319%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D60729119&h=e3002bde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200319&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=60729119</a>"},{"pid":"de4eae744736455f2f39b72a7a55a680fb75a2f1","tid":1933770,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/news/1646728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.premierleague.com%2Fnews%2F1646728&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=ca98aa15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.premierleague.com/news/1646728</a>"}]}